text: 3rd Rock from the Sun is an American television sitcom created by Bonnie and Terry Turner. It originally aired from January 9, 1996 to May 22, 2001 on NBC. ==Other websites== * Category:NBC network series Category:English-language television programs Category:1996 American television series debuts Category:2001 American television series endings Category:1990s American sitcoms Category:2000s American sitcoms
